# Mobile: React Native (Index)

## Rule files (by concern)

- `components.mdc`: component patterns and boundaries
- `performance.mdc`: list rendering and re-render controls
- `navigation.mdc`: React Navigation structure and typed routes
- `networking.mdc`: API client boundaries and error mapping
- `state.mdc`: Zustand/Redux Toolkit patterns and state organization
- `error_handling.mdc`: error boundaries, try-catch, Result/Either pattern
- `accessibility.mdc`: screen readers, a11y props, dynamic type support
- `testing.mdc`: Jest, React Native Testing Library, E2E tests
- `security.mdc`: secure storage, token management, SSL pinning
